uation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathcolor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgb(34 12 64 / 0.6)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathcolor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgba(34 12 64 / 0.3)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathcolor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgb(34.0 12 64 / 60%)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathcolor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>rgba(34.6 12 64 / 30%)<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- &lt;hsl()&gt; values --&gt;</span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>math</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">mathcolor</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span